trends: There has been one other sighting in Palm Beach Gardens
There were no other sightings in Palm Beach Gardens on or around August 31st 2013
divs: Sighting DetailsI was at the 8-31-2013 monthly launch of the florida Spacemodeling Assocation at Dyer park in west palm beach florida, we were looking sky ward for a model rocket that was just launched whren we first say this object. this objet had to be at an altude of over 25,000 ft. it was far above the clouds that were in the area. someone pointed out that there was also a plane in the same area as the object. then I noticed a small speck that flashed in the sun. I assumed that was the plane. this object was viewed by a number of people including, a comerical pilot and several USAF cadets.also one man tried to focus in on the objet with a telephoto lens but the objet was so far away that you could not make out the shape. the reaction to this object was pretty much what is that, a balloon, what?I followed the obnject untill it was gone over the top of a very high cloud. if I had to guess I would say that this was something that NASA was testing. N.R.M.
